<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.9">
<l>nallai neñcē nāntoḻutum nammuṭai namperumāṉ</l>
<l>alli mātar pulkaniṉṟa vāyiran tōḷaṉiṭam</l>
<l>nelli malkik kalluṭaippap pullilai yārttatarvāyc</l>
<l>cilli cilleṉ ṟollaṟāta ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the one with one-thousand arms who stays</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the lady of the lotus may embrace [him],</l>
<l>Oh, good heart, our own great lord whom we worship,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain where the sound of crickets trilling never ceases</l>
<l>Along dusty paths with grass rustling as gooseberry [roots] grow</l>
<l rend="indent">and break up boulders.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
